<title>HUNGARY: Richter soars, closes at new record.</title>
<headline>Richter soars, closes at new record.</headline>
<dateline>BUDAPEST 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hungarian pharmaceuticals maker Richter Gedeon Rt continued its bull run on Thursday on the Budapest bourse, finishing at a new record high of 14,950 forints, up 500, traders said.</p>
<p>But traders said the rally was a little surprising despite recently reported strong first quarter earnings by the company and before the company's new share offer this month.</p>
<p>&quot;This price is surprising because the company will issue shares in May,&quot; one trader said.</p>
<p>-- Budapest newsroom +36 1 327-4040</p>
